    <record name="GroupMtd" c:type="GstAnalyticsGroupMtd" version="1.30">
      <doc xml:space="preserve" filename="src/gst/metadata/gstanalyticsgroupmtd.c" line="28">This type of metadata define a group of #GstAnalyticsMtd. It allows to
describe results as composition. Group members are ordered within the group
and the @semantic_tag allow to define a specific group meaning.
For example with a semantic_tag = "posture/hand-21-kp", first
member represent the "wrist", second is the thumb first joint.</doc>
